**Obstructions** | Ability Type
__Basics__
Obstructions are another type of ability which aids in hiding from investigative powers. Instead of disguising a specific player, obstructions affect all results of affected investigative roles in some way.
__Details__
If not explicitly listed otherwise, every role is not affected by obstructions.

For a complete list of obstructions check `$i obstructions list`.

__Simplified__
Obstructions are another type of ability which aids in hiding from investigative powers. Instead of disguising a specific player, obstructions affect all results of affected investigative roles in some way.
